On 19 Mar, Stefan Richter wrote:
> Discard self ID buffer contents if
>   - the selfIDError flag is set,
>   - any of the self ID packets has bit errors.
> 
> Signed-off-by: Stefan Richter <stefanr@s5r6.in-berlin.de>
